Definition.Document:
Filtering Criteria Entry Page

Summary statistics will be aggregated in scorecards for a "filtered" period where we can apply a flow rate range to limit the data to - this can be helpful in only viewing "steady state" conditions.

DATA ENTRY VIEW

Open these 2 items and edit as needed to change filtering

  • FILTERING Flow Rate (Pipeline 1)
  • FILTERING Flow Rate Bandwith (Pipeline 1)

 

A condition will be edited based on these changes, which will apply filtering on other signals in this analysis.
